                <h1>Understanding Patient Background for Better Care</h1>
                <p>Patient background refers to the medical, social, and family history of individuals receiving healthcare. It helps healthcare professionals understand factors that may affect diagnosis and treatment. Key elements include past illnesses, medications, lifestyle choices, and relevant family medical history, which inform personalized care strategies.</p>
